parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delamination of Touchscreen Radio/Navigation/Heating and Cooling System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination of the touchscreen can cause unwanted button actions, distractions while driving, and loss of control over various vehicle features, leading to safety hazards.
symptoms: The screen delaminates
causing buttons to be pushed randomly
changing stations
favorites
and climate settings
making random phone calls
and displaying distracting sounds and visuals. The system may also shut down and restart randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning UConnect system can cause distractions while driving, loss of control over vehicle features, and safety hazards.
symptoms: The system periodically goes berserk
changing radio settings
flashing on the screen
and causing the backup camera to stay on. The system may also shut down and restart randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can cause vision impairment issues, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The backup camera screen stays on a black screen
flickers
or flashes
making it difficult or impossible to see behind the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical issues can cause distractions while driving, loss of control over vehicle features, and safety hazards.
symptoms: The radio only plays one station
Bluetooth and Apple CarPlay do not work
the radio volume does not function
and the system may produce loud noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected deployment of airbags can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The airbags deploy without any impact
causing sudden and unexpected distractions while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ECM module can cause the battery to drain, leading to safety hazards and inconvenience.
symptoms: The ECM module drains the battery
requiring a full discharge with battery cables removed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the vehicle to start can cause inconvenience and safety hazards.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to start
requiring jumpstarting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination of the LCD screen can cause the control of the radio, air conditioning, navigation, and other features to become dysfunctional, leading to driver distraction and potential safety hazards.
symptoms: The screen randomly beeps
changes air temperatures
starts navigation
causes loss of hands-free communication
clicks on icons randomly
makes unwanted calls
and switches radio stations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The warping and separation of the door panels can cause the side airbags to not deploy correctly and may interfere with the operation of the door locks, potentially leading to safety risks.
symptoms: The door panels are falling apart
warping
and popping out
and may cover the lock or obstruct the view from the side view mirror.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and distraction for the driver and passengers, potentially leading to safety risks.
symptoms: The air conditioning system does not cool the car after reaching a certain temperature
and may not blow cool air when the car sits for a while.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the radio and rear camera can cause driver distraction and potentially lead to safety risks.
symptoms: The radio freezes up and goes black
stopping the use of the rear camera.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination and warping of door panels can cause the door locks to malfunction, leading to safety risks and potential injuries. Additionally, it can also lead to airbag deployment issues, further increasing the risk of injury.
symptoms: Door panels detaching from the door frame
warped panels
delamination above the lock pin
obstructed locking pin
peeling or coming apart of interior molding
exposure of the inside of the door.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front bumper can cause it to hang lower or detach, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Front bumper hanging lower on one side
front bumper about to come off
repeated repairs and replacements of the bumper.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause glass fragments to fall on occupants, leading to injuries.
symptoms: Sunroof shattering without warning
sudden and unexpected breakage of the sunroof glass.
